# Haggerty Construction

> Haggerty Construction is a family-owned general contracting company based in St. George, Utah, specializing in custom kitchen remodels, bespoke cabinetry, bathroom renovations, and general contracting services throughout Washington County.

## About

Haggerty Construction was founded by William Haggerty, a construction professional with decades of experience. The company is operated by his three sons — Jayden, Blake, and Shjon — who grew up in St. George and are deeply committed to the local community. With over 30 years of combined experience, Haggerty Construction is known for quality craftsmanship, transparent communication, and exceptional customer service.

## Services

- Kitchen Remodels: Complete kitchen transformations including layout redesign, countertops, backsplash, and finishes
- Custom Cabinetry: Design, fabrication, and installation of custom cabinets for kitchens, bathrooms, laundry rooms, and living spaces
- Custom Storage Solutions: Floating shelves, built-in shelving, closet systems, and appliance garages
- Appliance Installation: Complex installations including built-in refrigerators with custom panels, pro ranges, vent hoods, and appliance garages with retractable doors
- Bathroom Renovations: Full bathroom remodels including vanities, tile, fixtures, and custom storage
- Home Additions: Room additions and structural modifications
- General Contracting: Full project management from design through completion

## Service Area

St. George, Washington, Hurricane, Ivins, Santa Clara, LaVerkin, Leeds — all of Washington County, Utah.

